function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

Hydra.PlayerGrantPotionDose(idActorPlayer, -1)

	idCloneDGN = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_dungeon, true)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCloneDGN) then
	
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idCloneDGN)
	
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCloneDGN, loc_NpcWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", false)
		
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idCloneDGN, 1.0)
			
	end

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idCloneMateen = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_questgiver_end, true)
	idCloneDerin = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(npc_questgiver_Derin, true)

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCloneMateen) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idCloneDerin) then
	
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idCloneMateen)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idCloneDerin)

		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idCloneDerin, "NPC_NonCombat_HTH_Wounded")
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idCloneMateen, "NPC_Basic")
		
	
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCloneMateen, loc_WalkTo_Mateen, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCloneDerin, loc_WalkTo_Derin, "NPC_Walk", false)
		
		
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idCloneMateen, 1.0)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idCloneDerin, 1.0)
			
	end


end
